description:
We’ve got murders! We’ve got relationship deal-breakers! We’ve got a wild new TWO PART crossover episode of Unqualified with Karen Kilgariff and Georgia Hardstark (My Favorite Murder). In Part 1, Karen tells the gang the tale of the BTK Killer, a man that would bind, torture, and kill his victim and they find out which notorious serial killer Anna’s uncle lived across the street from! Then Anna and Sim ask the girls their thoughts on relationship deal-breakers. Later, the group calls Katy, who is bothered by her boyfriend’s co-worker’s snide comments about her relationship with her boyfriend. Tune in for a fun and morbid time!
